[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Pass everything numeric through this helper before any
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     PutItem, BatchWriteItem, or UpdateItem call. Pandas and numpy
