[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    767[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # 1c. Tag the encounter context. Inpatient and emergency
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    768[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # results are tagged acute and excluded from chronic-trend
