[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         deviation    = latest_value - baseline_value
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # Approximate p-value from the filter's uncertainty: the
