[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Registry that maps detector names to instances. Production loads
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # this from the model registry and the per-LOINC catalog drives
